section(class="template-wrapper act_13" ng-init="s_actividad = 1" )

    aside(class="template-asideLeft o-aside-Item")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="1" ng-click="s_actividad = 1" ng-class="(s_actividad == 1) ? 'is-active' : '';")
        button(class="c-btn-IconAction" data-activities-count="2" ng-click="s_actividad = 2" ng-class="(s_actividad == 2) ? 'is-active' : '';")
        |
        |
    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")
            div(class="row-flex s-actividad u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 1")
                div(class="row")
                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres")
                        div(class="row")
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--thead")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--th") Expressing Opinions
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--td") I think... #[br] As far as I’m concerned... #[br] To my mind... #[br] According to me... #[br] As I see it... #[br] It seems to me that... #[br] In my point of view / my opinion... #[br] From my point of view...#[br] I am of the opinion that... #[br] I take the view that... #[br] My personal view is that... #[br] In my experience... #[br] As far as I understand / can see/see it... #[br] I think/believe that...
                        div(class="row")
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--thead")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--th") Agreeing with ideas
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--td")  I agree with this opinion. #[br] I completely agree with this view. #[br] This is absolutely right. #[br] I couldn’t / can’t agree more.
                        div(class="row")
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--thead")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--th") Partial Agreement
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--td") I agree with this point of view, but... #[br] This idea is right, but... #[br] I agree with you, but...
                        div(class="row")
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--thead")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--th") Disagreeing
                            div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody")
                                div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--tbody--tr")
                                    div(class="c-table-estilo_tres--td") I’m afraid… #[br] I can’t agree with you. #[br] I disagree with you. #[br] I don’t agree with you. #[br] I’m not sure I agree with you.

            div(class="row-flex s-actividad u-animationFadeDown" ng-show="s_actividad == 2")
                div(class="row")
                    h5 Decide if the speakers agree or disagree.
                    div(class="row-flex align-items-center")
                        div(class="col-flex-sm12 col-flex-md6 ta-c")
                            img(src="unit_3/module_10/assets/images/act_13_1.png", alt="act_13" class="u-responsive-img max-ancho350")

                        div(class="col-flex-sm12 col-flex-md6 col-center")
                                div(class="row-flex mb20 justify-center align-items-center")
                                    button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconListen is-active u-textWhite xs3 md1 max-h50" ng-audio="unit_3/module_10/assets/audios/act_13_1.mp3")
                                    div(class="col xs6 ta-c")
                                        h6.ta-c "Conversation 1"
                                        select(name="act_12_2" class="c-select")
                                            option(value="" disabled selected) 
                                            option(value="1") disagree
                                            option(value="2") agree
                                            option(value="3") partially agree
                            
                                div(class="row-flex mb20 justify-center align-items-center")
                                    button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconListen  is-active u-textWhite xs3 md1 max-h50" ng-audio="unit_3/module_10/assets/audios/act_13_2.mp3")
                                    div(class="col xs6 ta-c")
                                        h6.m-a "Conversation 2"
                                        select(name="act_12_2" class="c-select")
                                            option(value="" disabled selected) 
                                            option(value="1") disagree
                                            option(value="2") agree
                                            option(value="3") partially agree
                            
                                div(class="row-flex mb20 justify-center align-items-center")
                                    button(class="c-btn-IconAction u-bgIconListen  is-active u-textWhite  xs3 md1 max-h50" ng-audio="unit_3/module_10/assets/audios/act_13_3.mp3")
                                    div(class="col xs6 ta-c")
                                        h6.m-a "Conversation 3"
                                        select(name="act_12_2" class="c-select")
                                            option(value="" disabled selected) 
                                            option(value="1") disagree
                                            option(value="2") agree
                                            option(value="3") partially agree

                                   
                               
                                                
                            
                                    

